The Bank of England said it provided themarket with further assistance during the afternoon, buyingbills worth 166 mln stg at the lower rates introduced thismorning.    It bought 45 mln stg of local authority bills plus 27 mlnstg of bank bills in band one at 10-3/8 pct together with 94mln stg of band two bank bills at 10-5/16 pct.    The bank also revised its estimate of the market shortageup to 300 mln stg from 250 mln this morning. It has given totalassistance of 213 mln stg today. REUTER&#3;